{"data":[{"name":"70:1","price":"有人曾请求一种将发生的刑罚。","arabic":"سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5376,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"sa-ala sāilun biʿadhābin wāqiʿin ","translations":["Asked","a questioner","about a punishment","bound to happen","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["sa-ala","sāilun","biʿadhābin","wāqiʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,3789],[3,3789,6089],[4,6089,7264]]}},{"name":"70:2","price":"那是为不信的人们而预定的，没有任何人能加以抵抗。","arabic":"لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5377,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"lil'kāfirīna laysa lahu dāfiʿun ","translations":["To the disbelievers","not","of it","any preventer","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["lil'kāfirīna","laysa","lahu","dāfiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1730],[2,1730,2520],[3,2520,3080],[4,3080,4395]]}},{"name":"70:3","price":"那是安拉——天梯的主宰——发出的，","arabic":"مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5378,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-lahi dhī al-maʿāriji ","translations":["From","Allah","Owner","(of) the ways of ascent","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-lahi","dhī","al-maʿāriji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1430],[3,1430,1620],[4,1620,2935]]}},{"name":"70:4","price":"众天使和精神在一日之内升到他那里。那一日的长度是五万年。","arabic":"تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5379,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿruju al-malāikatu wal-rūḥu ilayhi fī yawmin kāna miq'dāruhu khamsīna alfa sanatin ","translations":["Ascend","the Angels","and the Spirit","to Him","in","a Day","[is]","its measure","(is) fifty","thousand","year(s)","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taʿruju","al-malāikatu","wal-rūḥu","ilayhi","fī","yawmin","kāna","miq'dāruhu","khamsīna","alfa","sanatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,3970],[3,3970,4970],[4,4970,5780],[5,5780,6210],[6,6210,7900],[7,7900,8480],[8,8480,9920],[9,9920,10990],[10,10990,11580],[11,11580,12765]]}},{"name":"70:5","price":"你安然地忍受吧。","arabic":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5380,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-iṣ'bir ṣabran jamīlan ","translations":["So be patient","a patience","good","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-iṣ'bir","ṣabran","jamīlan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,780],[2,780,2270],[3,2270,3965]]}},{"name":"70:6","price":"他们以为那刑罚是很远的，","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5381,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum yarawnahu baʿīdan ","translations":["Indeed, they","see it","(as) far off","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","yarawnahu","baʿīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2910],[3,2910,4165]]}},{"name":"70:7","price":"我却以为那是很近的。","arabic":"وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5382,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wanarāhu qarīban ","translations":["But We see it","near","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wanarāhu","qarīban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2705]]}},{"name":"70:8","price":"在那日天像熔铜，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5383,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma takūnu al-samāu kal-muh'li ","translations":["(The) Day ","will be","the sky","like molten copper","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","takūnu","al-samāu","kal-muh'li",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1460],[3,1460,3880],[4,3880,5275]]}},{"name":"70:9","price":"山像彩绒。","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5384,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"watakūnu al-jibālu kal-ʿih'ni ","translations":["And will be","the mountains","like wool","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["watakūnu","al-jibālu","kal-ʿih'ni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,2150],[3,2150,3525]]}},{"name":"70:10","price":"亲戚相见不相问。","arabic":"وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5385,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yasalu ḥamīmun ḥamīman ","translations":["And not","will ask","a friend","(about) a friend","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yasalu","ḥamīmun","ḥamīman",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1430],[3,1430,2460],[4,2460,4095]]}},{"name":"70:11","price":"他们眼看着他们，罪人愿意赎取那日的刑罚，即使牺牲他的儿女、","arabic":"يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5386,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yubaṣṣarūnahum yawaddu al-muj'rimu law yaftadī min ʿadhābi yawmi-idhin bibanīhi ","translations":["They will be made to see each other","Would wish","the criminal","if","he (could be) ransomed","from","(the) punishment","(of) that Day","by his children","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["yubaṣṣarūnahum","yawaddu","al-muj'rimu","law","yaftadī","min","ʿadhābi","yawmi-idhin","bibanīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2540],[2,2540,3300],[3,3300,4290],[4,4290,4680],[5,4680,5750],[6,5750,6080],[7,6080,6940],[8,6940,8870],[9,8870,12485]]}},{"name":"70:12","price":"他的妻子、他的弟兄，","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5387,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣāḥibatihi wa-akhīhi ","translations":["And his spouse","and his brother","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣāḥibatihi","wa-akhīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1810],[2,1810,4775]]}},{"name":"70:13","price":"和那收容他的血族，","arabic":"وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5388,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wafaṣīlatihi allatī tu'wīhi ","translations":["And his nearest kindred","who","sheltered him","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wafaṣīlatihi","allatī","tu'wīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,2420],[3,2420,5215]]}},{"name":"70:14","price":"以及大地上所有的人，但愿那能拯救自己。","arabic":"وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5389,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"waman fī al-arḍi jamīʿan thumma yunjīhi ","translations":["And whoever","(is) on","the earth","all","then","it (could) save him","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["waman","fī","al-arḍi","jamīʿan","thumma","yunjīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,1440],[3,1440,2260],[4,2260,4089],[5,4089,5439],[6,5439,9824]]}},{"name":"70:15","price":"绝不然，那确是发焰的烈火，","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5390,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahā laẓā ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, it (is)","surely a Flame of Hell","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahā","laẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2550],[2,2550,4360],[3,4360,5575]]}},{"name":"70:16","price":"能揭去头皮，","arabic":"نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5391,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"nazzāʿatan lilshawā ","translations":["A remover","of the skin of the head","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["nazzāʿatan","lilshawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2775]]}},{"name":"70:17","price":"能召唤转身而逃避的人。","arabic":"تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5392,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"tadʿū man adbara watawallā ","translations":["Inviting","(him) who","turned his back","and went away","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["tadʿū","man","adbara","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1240],[3,1240,2130],[4,2130,3475]]}},{"name":"70:18","price":"他曾聚积财产而加以保藏，","arabic":"وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5393,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wajamaʿa fa-awʿā ","translations":["And collected","and hoarded","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wajamaʿa","fa-awʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,2125]]}},{"name":"70:19","price":"人确是被造成浮躁的，","arabic":"۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5394,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-insāna khuliqa halūʿan ","translations":["Indeed","the man","was created","anxious ","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-insāna","khuliqa","halūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,3260],[3,3260,3960],[4,3960,5595]]}},{"name":"70:20","price":"遭遇灾殃的时候是烦恼的，","arabic":"إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5395,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā massahu al-sharu jazūʿan ","translations":["When","touches him","the evil","distressed","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","massahu","al-sharu","jazūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1350],[3,1350,2160],[4,2160,3755]]}},{"name":"70:21","price":"获得财富的时候是吝啬的。","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5396,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā massahu al-khayru manūʿan ","translations":["And when","touches him","the good","withholding","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","massahu","al-khayru","manūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1610],[3,1610,2460],[4,2460,3925]]}},{"name":"70:22","price":"只有礼拜的人们，〔不是那样〕，","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5397,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"illā al-muṣalīna ","translations":["Except","those who pray ","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","al-muṣalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,3765]]}},{"name":"70:23","price":"他们是常守拜功的；","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5398,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim dāimūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","at","their prayer","(are) constant","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","dāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1560],[3,1560,2050],[4,2050,3430],[5,3430,7895]]}},{"name":"70:24","price":"他们的财产中有一个定份，","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5399,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna fī amwālihim ḥaqqun maʿlūmun ","translations":["And those who","in","their wealth","(is) a right","known","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","fī","amwālihim","ḥaqqun","maʿlūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2820],[3,2820,4090],[4,4090,4770],[5,4770,8485]]}},{"name":"70:25","price":"是用于施济乞丐和贫民的；","arabic":"لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5400,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"lilssāili wal-maḥrūmi ","translations":["For the one who asks","and the deprived","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["lilssāili","wal-maḥrūmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2780],[2,2780,6375]]}},{"name":"70:26","price":"他们是承认报应之日的；","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5401,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna yuṣaddiqūna biyawmi al-dīni ","translations":["And those who","accept (the) truth","(of the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","yuṣaddiqūna","biyawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1200],[2,1200,2510],[3,2510,3360],[4,3360,5925]]}},{"name":"70:27","price":"他们是畏惧他们的养主的刑罚的。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5402,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum min ʿadhābi rabbihim mush'fiqūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of","(the) punishment","(of) their Lord","(are) fearful ","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","min","ʿadhābi","rabbihim","mush'fiqūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1200],[2,1200,1560],[3,1560,2630],[4,2630,3430],[5,3430,4850],[6,4850,8745]]}},{"name":"70:28","price":"他们的养主的刑罚，确是难保不降临的。","arabic":"إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5403,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿadhāba rabbihim ghayru mamūnin ","translations":["Indeed","(the) punishment","(of) your Lord","(is) not","to be felt secure (of) ","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿadhāba","rabbihim","ghayru","mamūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1890],[3,1890,2820],[4,2820,3470],[5,3470,6505]]}},{"name":"70:29","price":"他们是保守贞操的，","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5404,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum lifurūjihim ḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","their modesty","(are) guardians","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","lifurūjihim","ḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,1490],[3,1490,2880],[4,2880,5955]]}},{"name":"70:30","price":"除非对自己的妻子和奴婢，他们确是不因此而受责备的；","arabic":"إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5405,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ʿalā azwājihim aw mā malakat aymānuhum fa-innahum ghayru malūmīna ","translations":["Except","from","their spouses","or","what","they possess","rightfully","then indeed, they","(are) not","blameworthy","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ʿalā","azwājihim","aw","mā","malakat","aymānuhum","fa-innahum","ghayru","malūmīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,2980],[3,2980,4420],[4,4420,4790],[5,4790,5170],[6,5170,5970],[7,5970,7340],[8,7340,9170],[9,9170,9750],[10,9750,12705]]}},{"name":"70:31","price":"凡在这个范围之外有所要求的人，都是过分的。","arabic":"فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5406,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"famani ib'taghā warāa dhālika fa-ulāika humu al-ʿādūna ","translations":["But whoever","seeks","beyond","that","then those","[they]","(are) the transgressors ","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["famani","ib'taghā","warāa","dhālika","fa-ulāika","humu","al-ʿādūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1440],[3,1440,3500],[4,3500,4240],[5,4240,6759],[6,6759,7099],[7,7099,10094]]}},{"name":"70:32","price":"他们是尊重自己所受的信托，和自己所缔的盟约的；","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5407,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum li-amānātihim waʿahdihim rāʿūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of their trusts","and their promise","(are) observers","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","li-amānātihim","waʿahdihim","rāʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1540],[3,1540,3340],[4,3340,4420],[5,4420,7235]]}},{"name":"70:33","price":"他们是秉公作证的；","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5408,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum bishahādātihim qāimūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","in their testimonies","stand firm","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","bishahādātihim","qāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2060],[3,2060,3940],[4,3940,8905]]}},{"name":"70:34","price":"他们是谨守拜功的。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5409,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim yuḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","on","their prayer","keep a guard ","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","yuḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1600],[3,1600,2180],[4,2180,3350],[5,3350,7065]]}},{"name":"70:35","price":"这等人，是在乐园中受优待的。","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5410,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"ulāika fī jannātin muk'ramūna ","translations":["Those","(will be) in","Gardens","honored","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ulāika","fī","jannātin","muk'ramūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2530],[2,2530,2900],[3,2900,4920],[4,4920,8705]]}},{"name":"70:36","price":"不归信的人们，为何伸颈奔向你？","arabic":"فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5411,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"famāli alladhīna kafarū qibalaka muh'ṭiʿīna ","translations":["So what is with","those who","disbelieve","before you","(they) hasten","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["famāli","alladhīna","kafarū","qibalaka","muh'ṭiʿīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1700],[3,1700,2520],[4,2520,3390],[5,3390,6335]]}},{"name":"70:37","price":"三五成群的分列在你的左右呢？","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5412,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-yamīni waʿani al-shimāli ʿizīna ","translations":["On","the right","and on","the left","(in) separate groups","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-yamīni","waʿani","al-shimāli","ʿizīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1420],[3,1420,1990],[4,1990,2950],[5,2950,5635]]}},{"name":"70:38","price":"难道他们每个人都希望入恩泽的乐园吗？","arabic":"أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5413,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaṭmaʿu kullu im'ri-in min'hum an yud'khala jannata naʿīmin ","translations":["Does long","every","person","among them","that","he enters","a Garden","(of) Delight","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaṭmaʿu","kullu","im'ri-in","min'hum","an","yud'khala","jannata","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,1600],[3,1600,2250],[4,2250,3800],[5,3800,5730],[6,5730,7380],[7,7380,10085]]}},{"name":"70:39","price":"绝不然！我确已用他们所知道的物质创造了他们。","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5414,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innā khalaqnāhum mimmā yaʿl