 alladhī yūʿadūna ","translations":["So leave them","(to) converse vainly","and amuse themselves","until","they meet","their Day","which","they are promised","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["fadharhum","yakhūḍū","wayalʿabū","ḥattā","yulāqū","yawmahumu","alladhī","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2130],[3,2130,3210],[4,3210,4030],[5,4030,5020],[6,5020,6070],[7,6070,6950],[8,6950,10115]]}},{"name":"70:43","price":"在那日，他们将从坟中出来奔走，他们好像奔到牌位一样，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَخۡرُجُونَ مِنَ ٱلۡأَجۡدَاثِ سِرَاعٗا كَأَنَّهُمۡ إِلَىٰ نُصُبٖ يُوفِضُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5418,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yakhrujūna mina al-ajdāthi sirāʿan ka-annahum ilā nuṣubin yūfiḍūna ","translations":["(The) Day","they will come out","from","the graves","rapidly","as if they (were)","to","a goal","hastening","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yakhrujūna","mina","al-ajdāthi","sirāʿan","ka-annahum","ilā","nuṣubin","yūfiḍūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1770],[3,1770,2140],[4,2140,3350],[5,3350,4950],[6,4950,6910],[7,6910,7510],[8,7510,8950],[9,8950,12385]]}},{"name":"70:44","price":"同时，他们身遭凌辱，不敢仰视。那是他们被警告的日子。","arabic":"خَٰشِعَةً أَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ تَرۡهَقُهُمۡ ذِلَّةٞۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلَّذِي كَانُواْ يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5419,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"khāshiʿatan abṣāruhum tarhaquhum dhillatun dhālika al-yawmu alladhī kānū yūʿadūna ","translations":["Humbled","their eyesights","will cover them","humiliation","That","(is) the Day","which","they were","promised","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["khāshiʿatan","abṣāruhum","tarhaquhum","dhillatun","dhālika","al-yawmu","alladhī","kānū","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2620],[3,2620,3740],[4,3740,5200],[5,5200,6050],[6,6050,6780],[7,6780,7800],[8,7800,8750],[9,8750,14165]]}}],"chapter":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al